---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — OpenInterstate">
  <section>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      OpenInterstate is a public data infrastructure project. It exists
      independently of any single application. Downstream consumers do not
      define the public contract.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Principles</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Use neutral public names</li>
      <li>Publish reproducible releases</li>
      <li>Keep lineage and attribution explicit</li>
      <li>Optimize for developers and GIS users first</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
